-- Toyota March U.S. sales fall 39 percent
-- 
-- Wed Apr 1, 2009 3:48pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/04/01/us-autos-sales-toyota-idUSTRE5306JN20090401

 

 DETROIT  (Reuters) - Toyota Motor Corp on Wednesday said March U.S. sales fell an adjusted 36.6 percent. Highlights: 

 * Says US Lexus unit sales fell 40.6 percent in March * Says US Toyota unit sales fell 36 percent in March * Says total US inventory down 26.6 percent in Q1 versus year earlier * Says total US vehicle sales 132,802 in March * Says US sales fell 39 percent in March unadjusted for selling days